<div class="section">
    <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>
        We share information only under these specific circumstances:
    </p>

    <h3>With Steam</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Public achievement data is displayed per your <span class="highlight">Steam privacy settings</span></li>
        <li>Only shares data explicitly authorized through Steam API permissions</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Service Providers</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Google Analytics (anonymized data only)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Legal Disclosures</h3>
    <ul>
