    <ul>
        <li>Explicit "Do Not Sell" option for California users in account preferences</li>
        <li>No sale of personal data as defined by CCPA Section 1798.140(t)(1)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Additional Protections</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Data minimization practices for cross-border transfers</li>
        <li>Encryption in transit and at rest for all international transfers</li>
    </ul>
</div>

